lead_paragraph: On a night when Howard Dean dropped out of the contest for Democratic committee chairman, Mr. Ellison said he would considering resigning from Congress to lead the party.

headline.print_headline: New Question for Ellison: Can He Rebuild Democrats While in Congress?
